                    | This project was inspired by a Chinese historical story called Hua Mulan. Mulan is one of the most well-known ancient legends in ancient China, and the ballad of Mulan has been told in school textbooks since the story was passed down by our ancestors. 
                .col-sm-6.col-sm-height.col-middle.sm-text-center
